cb7305b2-d8b5-4302-aff3-6cdd9212ca64.title: Sunshake
cb7305b2-d8b5-4302-aff3-6cdd9212ca64.description: Mechanics love a cold sunshake when thirsty

54d8ef21-357d-48a3-a66d-40446f6bb686.title: Veggie Burger
54d8ef21-357d-48a3-a66d-40446f6bb686.description: A vegetarian alternative. Fills up the hunger meter to the max

54d84731-d9ec-435d-bc9d-d48e0763b1bf.title: Pizza Burger
54d84731-d9ec-435d-bc9d-d48e0763b1bf.description: A mechanics favorite food. Fills up the hunger meter to the max

e243f642-6934-42bb-8cdd-f8ff1704d411.title: Revival Baguette
e243f642-6934-42bb-8cdd-f8ff1704d411.description: Feed your fallen friends to get them back on their feet and back in action

d4d68946-aa03-4b8f-b1af-96b81ad4e305.title: Gasoline
d4d68946-aa03-4b8f-b1af-96b81ad4e305.description: Used to power gas engines and thrusters

869d4736-289a-4952-96cd-8a40117a2d28.title: Water
869d4736-289a-4952-96cd-8a40117a2d28.description: Great for watering plants, unfortunately not good for drinking.

5530e6a0-4748-4926-b134-50ca9ecb9dcf.title: Component Kit
5530e6a0-4748-4926-b134-50ca9ecb9dcf.description: Use to upgrade interactive parts and unlock bots in the Mechanic Station

c7322cd1-3158-41d9-b15a-eff2f2f8d9f7.title: Paint Ammo
c7322cd1-3158-41d9-b15a-eff2f2f8d9f7.description: Load your Paint Tool and give your creations some color

3a3280e4-03b6-4a4d-9e02-e348478213c9.title: Glowstick
3a3280e4-03b6-4a4d-9e02-e348478213c9.description: Throw them at night or other dark places to see things better

9a3e478c-2224-44fa-887c-239965bd05ad.title: Soil Bag
9a3e478c-2224-44fa-887c-239965bd05ad.description: Use them on the ground to place your seeds in

056e5ff1-f030-40df-946a-b830bf494c92.title: Gas Container
056e5ff1-f030-40df-946a-b830bf494c92.description: Can stores more gas and loads gas in to Gas Engines and other interactive parts that require Gas when connected

ea10d1af-b97a-46fb-8895-dfd1becb53bb.title: Water Container
ea10d1af-b97a-46fb-8895-dfd1becb53bb.description: Connect it to a Vacuum Pump that is under water to fil the Water Container with water

76331bbf-abbd-4b8d-bb54-f721a5b6193b.title: Fertilizer Container
76331bbf-abbd-4b8d-bb54-f721a5b6193b.description: Place furtilizer and connect it to a Vacuum Pump with a trigger to shoot furtilizer on to plants

da4833fd-f981-4e08-a9f7-48e630a7c146.title: Battery Container
da4833fd-f981-4e08-a9f7-48e630a7c146.description: Can Store more batteries and loads batteries in to Electric Engines and other interactive parts that require batteries when connected

096d4daf-639e-4947-a1a6-1890eaa94464.title: Potato Ammo Container
096d4daf-639e-4947-a1a6-1890eaa94464.description: Connect it to a Moutable Spud Gun with a trigger to shoot potato ammo

38ec258d-c644-4f08-8635-3f7434c884dd.title: Seed Container
38ec258d-c644-4f08-8635-3f7434c884dd.description: Place Seeds and connect it to a Vacuum Pump with a trigger to shoot seeds in to soil

ad35f7e6-af8f-40fa-aef4-77d827ac8a8a.title: Large Chest
ad35f7e6-af8f-40fa-aef4-77d827ac8a8a.description: Great for storing a lot of items. Can also be used with a Vacuum Pump

fcfae5e2-1df9-47d8-bb9a-30bec9b5b1f5.title: Chest
fcfae5e2-1df9-47d8-bb9a-30bec9b5b1f5.description: A simple chest to store your items.

2af00456-b22e-4743-b338-a91934aba7c5.title: Cookbot
2af00456-b22e-4743-b338-a91934aba7c5.description: Cooks delicious food that will fill up your health bar or revive fallen friends.

b63c6440-dfc2-4da7-acdb-3c385080b2e4.title: Craftbot
b63c6440-dfc2-4da7-acdb-3c385080b2e4.description: The Craftbot will help you craft everything from new blocks to useful interactive parts. A mechanics best friend.

5cb15c93-4fa9-48da-9974-2e95ca6c9e1c.title: Refinebot
5cb15c93-4fa9-48da-9974-2e95ca6c9e1c.description: Let the Refinebot help you out and refine all your collected logs. Put them in by hand or by placing a Resource Collector with logs next to it.

a930a42f-63ed-4fb0-933e-56ce8a889cc5.title: Resource Collector
a930a42f-63ed-4fb0-933e-56ce8a889cc5.description: Perfect for collecting and stacking logs. When full, place it next to a refinebot to turn logs in to blocks.

767a3121-2c31-473c-a5ab-27e188fdd55a.title: Dressbot
767a3121-2c31-473c-a5ab-27e188fdd55a.description: Use the Dressbot to make new clothes for your Mechanic. Just add your garment boxes and the right amount of cotton. You can also customise your look by using the blue wardrobe.

4a1b886b-913e-4aad-b5b6-6e41b0db23a6.title: Bearing
4a1b886b-913e-4aad-b5b6-6e41b0db23a6.description: Everything you place on the bearing will revolve. Bearings can also be connected to an engine or the driver's seat to be controlled in different ways.

7cf717d7-d167-4f2d-a6e7-6b2c70aa3986.title: Switch
7cf717d7-d167-4f2d-a6e7-6b2c70aa3986.description: Unlimited toggling on demand. The Switch activates whatever it's connected to, making it indispensible when you want to turn things on and off with a single push. It can activate an engine, a thruster, the controller and more.

1e8d93a4-506b-470d-9ada-9c0a321e2db5.title: Button
1e8d93a4-506b-470d-9ada-9c0a321e2db5.description: Activates stuff. The button activates as long as it remains pressed.

dfefc9d7-db03-4d25-ad85-eae1d824d8c0.title: Radio
dfefc9d7-db03-4d25-ad85-eae1d824d8c0.description:
All hits, all the time. Those beastly bots have hijacked and are now transmitting classic selections from their deeply unusual taste in music. Activate it by interacting with it
or by connecting it to a trigger.

818f4e15-ff51-4fed-b874-723a25d62e1c.title: Horn
818f4e15-ff51-4fed-b874-723a25d62e1c.description: Add it to your vehicle or use it as a door bell. Honk at your friends to avoid accidents. Set the pitch and connect it to a trigger to activate it.

9f0f56e8-2c31-4d83-996c-d00a9b296c3f.title: Logic Gate
9f0f56e8-2c31-4d83-996c-d00a9b296c3f.description: The Logic Gate is a powerful block that allows you to build basic logical functions. By pressing E on the block, the mechanic can choose between different logic gate types. The logic gate can be connected to other logic gates, triggers, timers and more. Great for making advanced creations.

8f7fd0e7-c46e-4944-a414-7ce2437bb30f.title: Timer
8f7fd0e7-c46e-4944-a414-7ce2437bb30f.description: The Timer allows you delay the interaction between two interactive parts. For example, between a switch and a controller. It goes great with Logic Gates.

161786c1-1290-4817-8f8b-7f80de755a06.title: Totebot Head: Bass
161786c1-1290-4817-8f8b-7f80de755a06.description: This robot head is broken. But the sound generator inside seems to still be working. Creative mechanics can probably find a way to make music with this.

4c6e27a2-4c35-4df3-9794-5e206fef9012.title: Totebot Head: Percussion
4c6e27a2-4c35-4df3-9794-5e206fef9012.description: This robot head is broken. But the sound generator inside seems to still be working. Creative mechanics can probably find a way to make music with this.

a052e116-f273-4d73-872c-924a97b86720.description: This robot head is broken. But the sound generator inside seems to still be working. Creative mechanics can probably find a way to make music with this.

1c04327f-1de4-4b06-92a8-2c9b40e491aa.description: This robot head is broken. But the sound generator inside seems to still be working. Creative mechanics can probably find a way to make music with this.

3efe715f-8745-475f-a609-5e7cbe09a8ef.description: Used for maximum relaxation. Sit down and relax or add it to your vehicle to stay nice and clean on the go. Can be connected to triggers which can activate other interactive parts from the bathtub.

ca003562-fde7-463c-969e-f8334ae54387.title: Toilet
ca003562-fde7-463c-969e-f8334ae54387.description: Used for avoiding standing. Take a seat and relax or add it to your vehicle so your friends can tag along. Can be connected to triggers which can activate other interactive parts from the toilet. Don't forget to flush!

4152ce33-9b43-4c51-80a3-e0b4fe38841d.title: Raft Shark Mount
4152ce33-9b43-4c51-80a3-e0b4fe38841d.description: A plastic shark mount prop from the survival game Raft. It seems to have some mechanical joints inside. Maybe it can bite?

8d3b98de-c981-4f05-abfe-d22ee4781d33.title: Small Explosive Canister
8d3b98de-c981-4f05-abfe-d22ee4781d33.description:
Highly explosive canister that can detonate by strong collisions or by Spud Guns
This canister has a small explosion radius.

24001201-40dd-4950-b99f-17d878a9e07b.title: Large Explosive Canister
24001201-40dd-4950-b99f-17d878a9e07b.description:
Highly explosive canister that can detonate by strong collisions or by Spud Guns
This canister has a large explosion radius.

7324219e-2b19-4098-baa3-9876984ead08.description: Extends and contracts! Connect it to a trigger to activate. The piston can also be connected to a controller to make it extend and contract in a sequence. Perfect for creating impressive creations.

2f004fdf-bfb0-46f3-a7ac-7711100bee0c.description: Extends and contracts! Connect it to a trigger to activate. The piston can also be connected to a controller to make it extend and contract in a sequence. Perfect for creating impressive creations.

97f449b6-c948-448b-b8b3-4448e3f6b956.title: Vacuum Pump
97f449b6-c948-448b-b8b3-4448e3f6b956.description: The Vaccum Pump has many uses when connected to a trigger. Suck up water in to a water container. Pick up plants in to a chest. It can even shoot and place items from a chest.

9b8f2abd-265c-4750-b8b9-fe6cb564633c.title: Vacuum Pipe
9b8f2abd-265c-4750-b8b9-fe6cb564633c.description: Use it with the Vacuum Pump to make items travel through pipes

5939f460-ab6c-48f2-9d07-a66845ce8cf2.title: Vacuum Pipe Corner
5939f460-ab6c-48f2-9d07-a66845ce8cf2.description: Use it with the Vacuum Pump to make items travel through pipes

5eb8975b-0acf-43a7-ab4e-62ce661c0df7.title: Respawn Bed
5eb8975b-0acf-43a7-ab4e-62ce661c0df7.description: Take a lovely nap in this comfy bed to respawn in it after your mechanic has been knocked out

69559e81-50fa-40ae-afa2-a22c1a49eb54.title: Water Cannon
69559e81-50fa-40ae-afa2-a22c1a49eb54.description: Connect it to a Water container with a trigger to water your plants more efficiently

454ad69d-bac2-4b06-9386-6267bcbfece2.title: Mountable Spud Gun
454ad69d-bac2-4b06-9386-6267bcbfece2.description: Connect it to a Ammo container with a trigger to shoot

c8b1bc7b-304e-44ce-9ca1-937b8e69d70c.title: Protector: Anti-Destruction
c8b1bc7b-304e-44ce-9ca1-937b8e69d70c.description: Helps protecting your creation from damage. Connect it to a Battery container

8fd2cf31-70b3-499a-bfb0-7e3d2c580258.title: Encryptor: Anti-Connection
8fd2cf31-70b3-499a-bfb0-7e3d2c580258.description: Hides the connections on your creations from other mechanics. Connect it to a Battery container

ed27f5e2-cac5-4a32-a5d9-49f116acc6af.title: Headlight
ed27f5e2-cac5-4a32-a5d9-49f116acc6af.description: Let there be visibility! Connect to a trigger to turn on and off. Adjustable beam range.

695d66c8-b937-472d-8bc2-f3d72dd92879.title: Warehouse Spotlight
695d66c8-b937-472d-8bc2-f3d72dd92879.description: Let there be visibility! Connect to a trigger to turn on and off. Adjustable beam range.

63695efd-0862-49f2-ace6-4d1758147fae.title: Garment Box (Common)
63695efd-0862-49f2-ace6-4d1758147fae.description: Use it in a Dressbot to make new clothes

27a221b1-9809-4df1-901a-caafe119c9b6.title: Garment Box (Rare)
27a221b1-9809-4df1-901a-caafe119c9b6.description: Use it in a Dressbot to make new clothes

7ab0cac7-b055-4283-b0bc-f85dd4d0416b.title: Garment Box (Epic)
7ab0cac7-b055-4283-b0bc-f85dd4d0416b.description: Use it in a Dressbot to make new clothes

bfcfac34-db0f-42d6-bd0c-74a7a5c95e82.title: Potato
bfcfac34-db0f-42d6-bd0c-74a7a5c95e82.description: A starchy Potato. Can also be used as ammo for spud guns and mountable spud guns.

3e10ef67-383a-4b60-aa5b-b1173134e437.title: Saw Blade
3e10ef67-383a-4b60-aa5b-b1173134e437.description: Cut down trees faster with the Saw Blade. Put it on a bearing that is connected to a engine and drive it in to a tree.

276fd55b-ae54-4a7a-ace6-fddd2d3370a5.title: Drill
276fd55b-ae54-4a7a-ace6-fddd2d3370a5.description: Use the Drill to mine square rocks for stone and metal. Put it on a bearing that is connected to a engine and drive it in to a square rock.

c96ab903-f238-4bae-a614-28a758716d00.title: Scrap Gas Engine
c96ab903-f238-4bae-a614-28a758716d00.description: An engine with uneven speed and adjustable power, ideally suited to powering vehicles. Can be connected to a driver's seat or trigger. This Engine is not upgradable.

bd597ac9-6640-43ba-9bd8-ed584a794f13.title: Scrap Driver's Seat
bd597ac9-6640-43ba-9bd8-ed584a794f13.description: Makes bearings turn left and right. Can be connected to an engine to control the direction of travel. Can also be connected to triggers that can be activated from the seat. This Drive's Seat is not upgradable.

847daf20-02bf-4170-8699-9ab106acd29a.title: Scrap Seat
847daf20-02bf-4170-8699-9ab106acd29a.description: Used for avoiding standing. Take a seat and relax or add it to your vehicle so your friends can tag along. This Seat is not upgradable.

e49b210a-0d46-4f06-bcd8-08862379d156.title: Warehouse Key
e49b210a-0d46-4f06-bcd8-08862379d156.description: Used to activate a Warehouse elevator

c654a023-ca53-4109-9f18-d297c18e9a02.title: Master Battery
c654a023-ca53-4109-9f18-d297c18e9a02.description: Used to power on large spaceships or stations

798c2c81-1f8e-481b-8c32-b71b5dc5511a.title: Water Bucket
798c2c81-1f8e-481b-8c32-b71b5dc5511a.description: Fill it with water to water your plants.

c5ea0c2f-185b-48d6-b4df-45c386a575cc.title: Spud Gun
c5ea0c2f-185b-48d6-b4df-45c386a575cc.description: Spud Gun with single potato shot.

f6250bf4-9726-406f-a29a-945c06e460e5.title: Spud Shotgun
f6250bf4-9726-406f-a29a-945c06e460e5.description: Shoots sizzling hot fries in a spread.

9fde0601-c2ba-4c70-8d5c-2a7a9fdd122b.title: Spudling Gun
9fde0601-c2ba-4c70-8d5c-2a7a9fdd122b.description: Shoots potatoes in a rapid fire. Uses a lot of potato ammo

be744e84-f67e-4c06-a809-c247adc1babb.title: Master Switch
be744e84-f67e-4c06-a809-c247adc1babb.description: Unlimited toggling on demand. The Switch activates whatever it's connected to, making it indispensible when you want to turn things on and off with a single push. It can activate an engine, a thruster, the controller and more.

8f190ce2-3a59-423e-8483-a7aa67bd5bc0.title: Lift
8f190ce2-3a59-423e-8483-a7aa67bd5bc0.description: Build on the lift to create freely movable constructions that won't be fixed to the ground. Can be elevated and lowered as well as lift creations that have flipped over.
